== Damage Formulas ==

=== Dual Tech Damage ===

 Base = (Tech1_Power × Char1_Stat + Tech2_Power × Char2_Stat) × 1.2
 Final = Base × Element_Modifier × Random(0.9-1.1)

Dual techs receive a 1.2x multiplier over using techs separately.

=== Triple Tech Damage ===

 Base = (Tech1_Power × Stat1 + Tech2_Power × Stat2 + Tech3_Power × Stat3) × 1.5
 Final = Base × Element_Modifier × Random(0.9-1.1)

Triple techs receive a 1.5x multiplier.

